msgid "Beltoft Smart Discounts for WooCommerce - Pro requires the free \"Beltoft Smart Discounts for WooCommerce\" plugin to be installed and activated."
msgstr "O Beltoft Smart Discounts para WooCommerce - Pro requer que o plugin gratuito \"Beltoft Smart Discounts para WooCommerce\" esteja instalado e ativado."

msgid "Beltoft Smart Discounts for WooCommerce - Pro requires WooCommerce to be installed and activated."
msgstr "O Beltoft Smart Discounts para WooCommerce - Pro requer que o WooCommerce esteja instalado e ativado."

msgid "Beltoft Smart Discounts for WooCommerce - Pro requires version 1.0.0 or higher of the free plugin. Please update."
msgstr "O Beltoft Smart Discounts para WooCommerce - Pro requer a versão 1.0.0 ou superior do plugin gratuito. Por favor atualize."

